OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA woman accused of cutting her film
OL,8,Fdirector sister's throat and making
OL,9,Foff with her Rolex watch told her she
OL,10,Fwas "planning to kill" her months
OL,11,Fbefore, a court has heard.
OL,13,FNancy Pexton, 70, allegedly slashed
OL,14,Fand stabbed her sibling, Jennifer
OL,15,FAbbott, at her flat in Camden, north
OL,16,FLondon, on June 10 last year.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
