OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776041692
OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThree days later, a neighbour broke
OL,8,Fdown the door and found 69-year-old Ms
OL,9,FAbbott dead on the floor of her living
OL,10,Froom with gaffer tape covering her
OL,11,Fmouth.
OL,13,FThe victim's diamond-encrusted, gold,
OL,14,FRolex watch was missing and later
OL,15,Frecovered from Pexton's belongings
OL,16,Fafter she was admitted to hospital,
OL,17,Fjurors have heard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
