PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776041692
OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FOn Friday, prosecutor Bill Boyce KC
OL,8,Fread a message from Pexton to Ms
OL,9,FAbbott which the victim shared with
OL,10,Fher nephew in November 2024.
OL,12,FPexton wrote: "You know Jenny, I
OL,13,Falways loved you from my heart and you
OL,14,Fbetrayed me in every way because you
OL,15,Fjealous of me all the time since we
OL,16,Fwere kids and your jealousy turned to
OL,17,Fhate.
OL,19,F"You know I was planning to kill you
OL,20,Fbut it was just a thought, I would
OL,21,Fnever hurt you."
OL,26,@tD@OOU{D@AOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776041692
OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe message went on to warn Ms Abbott
OL,8,Fto "watch your back from those you
OL,9,Fconned and stole money from".
OL,11,FPexton wrote: "You never know they
OL,12,Fcould get you while you walking your
OL,13,Fdog. Be careful honey, I worry about
OL,14,Fyou. You so many enemy (sic)."
OL,16,FAt the time, Ms Abbott had told her
OL,17,Fnephew she thought Pexton was "capable
OL,18,Fof anything" and she feared for her
OL,19,Fsafety, the court heard.
OL,26,@pD@DOUqD@\O]sD@OOUvD@^O]yD@_OUzD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
