PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776041692
OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe allegedly told him Pexton had
OL,8,Fattempted to murder two of her
OL,9,Fboyfriends and hired two people to
OL,10,Fbeat up someone called David.
OL,12,FMs Abbott also asked her nephew if she
OL,13,Fshould apply for a restraining order
OL,14,Fand even wrote a note about it on a
OL,15,Fscrap of paper, jurors heard.
OL,17,FMr Boyce told jurors that Pexton's
OL,18,Fmessage her sister may have been
OL,19,Fcaused by hate coupled with "jealousy
OL,20,Fand abuse".
OL,26,@{D@]OU|D@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
