PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776041692
OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FExamination of Pexton's phone revealed
OL,8,Fa series of notes in which she
OL,9,Freferred to thinking about killing her
OL,10,Fsister and complained about other
OL,11,Ffamily members, the court was told.
OL,13,FThe day before Ms Abbott's death,
OL,14,FPexton messaged her: "Bless you, you
OL,15,Fsounded shocked that I'm coming to c u
OL,16,Fnow. Sorry I scared you Thursday or
OL,17,FFriday (sic)."
OL,19,FOn June 10, the defendant called her
OL,20,Fsister nine times, the final call
OL,21,Flasting just over 15 minutes.
OL,26,@vD@VOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
