CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776041692
OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Boyce said it was "no coincidence"
OL,8,FMs Abbott was not seen or heard from
OL,9,Fafter she took her corgi dog, Prince,
OL,10,Ffor a walk that morning.
OL,12,FHe alleged Pexton was the last person
OL,13,Fto see her alive having fatally
OL,14,Fattacked her in her home and leaving
OL,15,Fjust before 2pm.
OL,17,FPexton was arrested on June 18 after
OL,18,Fthe discovery of her sister's watch in
OL,19,Fher bag.
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
