PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776041692
OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe denied killing her sister and
OL,8,Fclaimed Ms Abbott had given her the
OL,9,FRolex to "keep for her", jurors heard.
OL,11,FIn prepared statements to police, she
OL,12,Fstated that she loved her sister and
OL,13,Fwould never harm her.
OL,15,FShe claimed the notes on her phone and
OL,16,Fmessage to Ms Abbott were examples of
OL,17,F"venting" her feelings.
OL,19,FShe stated: "I do not think my sister
OL,20,Fwas evil, I used that term just to
OL,21,Fvent but I did not mean it.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@WO]yD@AOUyD@IO]{D@MOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
