FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776041692
OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"My sister and I were very close and
OL,8,Fwe would have arguments like many
OL,9,Fsiblings but we would always make up
OL,10,Fand move on."
OL,12,FThe defendant claimed she got Ms
OL,13,FAbbott's blood on her clothes when she
OL,14,Fhugged her while the victim was having
OL,15,Fa nosebleed.
OL,17,FHowever, Mr Boyce said scientific
OL,18,Fanalysis supported the proposition
OL,19,Fthat she got covered in blood from
OL,20,Fstabbing Ms Abbott multiple times.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
