PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776041692
OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe told jurors an examination of Ms
OL,8,FAbbott's flat showed evidence that
OL,9,Fsomeone had tried to "clean up".
OL,11,FHe dismissed the defendant's claim
OL,12,Fthat Ms Abbott would have given away
OL,13,Fher "prized Rolex watch" which she
OL,14,Fnever took off.
OL,16,FHe said: "The reality, of course, is
OL,17,Fthat the defendant took the watch
OL,18,Fhaving stabbed her sister to do so."
OL,26,@qD@VOUqD@_O]uD@EOUuD@XO]xD@JOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
