OL,3,CWoman accused of murder told sister
OL,4,Cshe was 'planning to kill her', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FPexton, of no fixed address, has
OL,8,Fdenied murder and the Old Bailey trial
OL,9,Fcontinues.
